'''L'association La Faculté des études elfiques''', FEE, was a [[Tolkien Societies|Tolkien Society]] in France.

==History==
FEE was founded in 1985 by [[Édouard Kloczko]] and disbanded in 1993.<ref>http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%89tudes_sur_J._R._R._Tolkien#Associations_.C2.AB_loi_1901_.C2.BB</ref>

==Publications==
Publications included ''Féerik'' and ''Le Gollum illustré''.
